title: Triple J Hottest 100 of All Time (2009)
description:
The Hottest Songs of All Time as voted in Australia's (and the world's) biggest publicly voted music countdown. Run by Triple J (JJJ).

All files are mp3's ranging from 128 kbps to 320 kbps. 

For those who like a bit extra, keep an eye out for my next release which will have the recordings of the broadcast to re-live the moment. It will also include several music videos of winning entries.

Enjoy.
